---
import Navbar from "../../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import Modal from "../../components/Modal.astro";

---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport" />
    <title>Carl Manuel</title>
    <meta name="description" content="" />
    <meta name="keywords" content="" />

    <!-- Favicons -->
    <link href="/assets/img/logo.png" rel="icon" />
    <link href="/assets/img/apple-touch-icon.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" />

    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect" />
    <link href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,700;1,900&family=Poppins:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <!-- Vendor CSS Files -->
    <link
      href="/assets/vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link
      href="/assets/vendor/bootstrap-icons/bootstrap-icons.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link href="/assets/vendor/aos/aos.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link
      href="/assets/vendor/glightbox/css/glightbox.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link href="/assets/vendor/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />

    <!-- Main CSS File -->
    <link href="/assets/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet" />

    <!-- Inline CSS to Fix Project Information Positioning -->
  </head>

  <body class="portfolio-details-page">
    <Navbar />


    <main class="main">
      <!-- Page Title -->
      <div class="page-title accent-background">
        <div class="container">
          <h1>Carl Manuel</h1>
          <nav class="breadcrumbs">
            <ol>
              <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="/Projects">Projects</a></li>
              <li><a href="/PersonalProjects">Personal Projects</a></li>
              <li class="current">Carl Manuel</li>
            </ol>
          </nav>
        </div>
      </div><!-- End Page Title -->

      <!-- Portfolio Details Section -->
      <section id="portfolio-details" class="portfolio-details section">
        <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
          <div class="portfolio-details-slider swiper init-swiper">
            <script type="application/json" class="swiper-config">
              {
                "loop": true,
                "speed": 600,
                "autoplay": {
                  "delay": 5000
                },
                "slidesPerView": "auto",
                "navigation": {
                  "nextEl": ".swiper-button-next",
                  "prevEl": ".swiper-button-prev"
                },
                "pagination": {
                  "el": ".swiper-pagination",
                  "type": "bullets",
                  "clickable": true
                }
              }
            </script>
            <div class="swiper-wrapper align-items-center">
              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <img
                      src="/assets/img/personalProjectLogos/GregS/UI.png"
                  alt=""
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
            <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
            <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="row justify-content-between gy-4 mt-4">
            <div class="col-lg-8" data-aos="fade-up">
              <div class="portfolio-description">
                <h2>Overview</h2>
                <p>
                  The Carl Manuel app is a Streamlit-based chatbot that helps users interact with car manuals
through natural language. Users can upload a PDF manual, which is processed by extracting
and chunking the text using LangChain. These chunks are stored in a Chroma vector database
with OpenAI embeddings, enabling semantic search. On upload, the manual is assigned a
unique ID for future access, and error-safe persistence ensures smooth first-time storage. Users
can then ask questions about their manual, and the app retrieves relevant information using a
RetrievalQA chain with OpenAIâ€™s language model.
                </p>
                <br />
                <br />
                <div class="row align-items-center">
                  <div class="col-md-6 d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <img
                      src="/assets/img/personalProjectLogos/GregS/Feature1.png"
                      class="img-fluid zoomable-image"
                      style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; cursor: pointer;"
                      data-bs-toggle="modal"
                      data-bs-target="#imageModal"
                      onclick="setModalImage(this.src, this.alt)"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-6">
                    <p>
                      After the user uploads a manual, they can start entering their queries into the text field at the
bottom of the screen. The chatbot classifies the query into 3 different categories: manual_query
for queries related to the manual, general for car related queries that do not refer to something
that can be found in the manual, and unrelated which refers to queries unrelated to cars. The
chatbot then replies with the answer to the question.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <br />
                <br />

                <div class="row align-items-center">
                  <div
                    class="col-md-6 order-md-2 d-flex justify-content-center"
                  >
                    <img
                      src="/assets/img/personalProjectLogos/GregS/Feature2.png"
                      class="img-fluid zoomable-image"
                      style="max-width: 100%; height: auto; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; cursor: pointer;"
                      data-bs-toggle="modal"
                      data-bs-target="#imageModal"
                      onclick="setModalImage(this.src, this.alt)"
                    />
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
                    <p>
                      Users can use the dropdown menu to switch between different uploaded manuals. When they
select a different manual, they can then start sending questions to the chatbot that will base its
reply on the selected manual.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-3" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
              <div class="portfolio-info sticky">
                <h3>Project information</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li><strong>Developer</strong> KentzC</li>
                  <li><strong>Technology</strong> Python<br>LangChain<br>Streamlit</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div><!-- /Portfolio Details Section -->
        </div>

        <Footer />
        <Modal />

        <!-- Scroll Top -->
        <a
          href="#"
          id="scroll-top"
          class="scroll-top d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center"
          ><i class="bi bi-arrow-up-short"></i></a
        >

        <!-- Preloader -->
        <div id="preloader"></div>

        <!-- Vendor JS Files -->
        <script
          is:inline
          src="/assets/vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
        <script is:inline src="/assets/vendor/php-email-form/validate.js"
        ></script>
        <script is:inline src="/assets/vendor/aos/aos.js"></script>
        <script
          is:inline
          src="/assets/vendor/purecounter/purecounter_vanilla.js"></script>
        <script is:inline src="/assets/vendor/glightbox/js/glightbox.min.js"
        ></script>
        <script is:inline src="/assets/vendor/swiper/swiper-bundle.min.js"
        ></script>
        <script
          is:inline
          src="/assets/vendor/imagesloaded/imagesloaded.pkgd.min.js"></script>
        <script
          is:inline
          src="/assets/vendor/isotope-layout/isotope.pkgd.min.js"></script>

        <!-- Main JS File -->
        <script is:inline src="/assets/js/main.js"></script>
      </section>
    </main></body>
</html>
